author: China Insights
description:
An exclusive interview at Seoul with Mr. Hwang Kyo-Ahn, former Prime Minister and Acting President of South Korea.  Mr. Hwang highlighted the results of the current impeachment and criminal trials are unpredictable and “up to the heaven”.  And He emphasized that President Donald Trump once called him to emphasized that US-Korea Alliance is blood-bond. He also believe that Korean people are able to keep rational and peace in the current protests and differentiate CCP from Chinese residents so that there will be no anti-Chinese people crisis.

title: Exclusive Interview with Mr. Hwang Kyo-Ahn on President Moon’s Impeachment and US-Korea Alliance
